{"tid":692544,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"TL韓梓亮感謝粉絲不離不棄搞歌迷聚會","createTime":"2018-06-06T18:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T19:41:36.000Z","uid":1426,"like":19,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"963216e75dcc688d3f90ca5d63908aff46c046ac","tid":692544,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T18:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161128/photo/bkn-20161128025022365-1128_00862_001_01p.jpg?20161128092626\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20161128%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161128025022365-1128_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20161128092626&h=9d942af4&s={SIZE}\" />歌手韓梓亮（MAX.B）為慶祝出道10個月特別舉行歌迷聚會，有約20名歌迷出席，他表示非常開心，因自己不是有名氣偶像，故事前不知可會有歌迷到場，他連聲道謝說：「感謝歌迷一直對我不離不棄，一直支持我同守護我。」 <br />\n<br />\nMAX.B又謂曾經在網上有人留言攻擊他，但其歌迷即時在網上維護他，不停留言反擊攻擊者，令他受寵若驚，又說以往曾遭過不少網絡欺凌，有感網上駁火、對罵不是最佳解決問題方法，故唯有啞忍及自我反省，他說：「我覺得最好嘅解決方法，係自己繼續努力，做好自己，用音樂去證明自己。」 <br />\n<br />\n問到MAX.B將踏入新一年有何新願望，他表示：「嚟緊都係注重訓練，增值自己，稍後會跟吳浩學唱歌，又會不停學跳舞進修自己。」現時他已經錄好兩首歌，迄下正進入排舞階段，而新歌風格構思來自歐美style。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161128/bkn-20161128025022365-1128_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20161128%2Fbkn-20161128025022365-1128_00862_001.html&d=QJoBkUPcYLFhFRhK746dzp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=7ba1ce79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161128/bkn-20161128025022365-1128_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1d833387149bacf6d870dd5c13773e93125f0573","tid":692544,"uid":92376,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T18:16:16.000Z","msg":"20x$50=$1000"},{"pid":"eb492b49a4721ac6b07d83c97d10460f8a9e4b86","tid":692544,"uid":1426,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T18:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/093546_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thum