or: red;\">歌迷聚會</span>，有約20名歌迷出席，他表示非常開心，因自己不是有名氣偶像，<span style=\"color: red;\">故事前不知可會有歌迷到場</span>，他連聲道謝說：「感謝歌迷一直對我不離不棄，一直支持我同守護我。」 <br />\n<br />\nMAX.B又謂曾經在網上有人留言攻擊他，但其歌迷即時在網上維護他，不停留言反擊攻擊者，令他受寵若驚，又說以往曾遭過不少網絡欺凌，有感網上駁火、對罵不是最佳解決問題方法，故唯有啞忍及自我反省，他說：「我覺得最好嘅解決方法，係自己繼續努力，做好自己，用音樂去證明自己。」 <br />\n<br />\n問到MAX.B將踏入新一年有何新願望，他表示：「嚟緊都係注重訓練，增值自己，稍後會跟吳浩學唱歌，又會不停學跳舞進修自己。」現時他已經錄好兩首歌，迄下正進入排舞階段，而新歌風格構思來自歐美style。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161128/bkn-20161128025022365-1128_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20161128%2Fbkn-20161128025022365-1128_00862_001.html&d=QJoBkUPcYLFhFRhK746dzp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=7ba1ce79\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161128/bkn-20161128025022365-1128_00862_001.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">???????????</span>"},{"pid":"a9a9a5e71f5c5b0b1497b6f192b4c1adbb5648db","tid":692544,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T01:30:38.000Z","msg":"Max B 個名好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f308c32636f307e9f5a3356d28af71af3a2b741","tid":692544,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"775fcafc663ff3387a3760a802ad0572f88e9511","tid":692544,"uid":173208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"106ad980f402546c71629842991d04476bc20933","tid":692544,"uid":1426,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T18:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170702/photo/bkn-20170702041520085-0702_00862_001_03b.jpg?20170702032931\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170702%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170702041520085-0702_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20170702032931&h=ab18fe80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前左一 nben/蓋 左二 kalou"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T22:32:29.000Z","msg":"禿頭中坑<img 